odynamic co-transport in the presence of changes in\nfluorescence quantum yield. We believe this will be useful when studying\ninteracting systems exhibiting fluorescence quenching, enhancement or Forster\nresonance energy transfer with transport methods.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 18:18:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Feb 2017 17:58:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-24"}
