{(peak\\ time)}^{3/2}$. We show\nthat such a relation can be explained qualitatively (though not quantitatively)\nby a close connection between the growth of dark matter halos and their\ngalaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 19:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2017 17:33:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-11"}
