 implications of our results on the\neffectiveness of the minimum bandwidth constraint on influencing small-cell\ndeployments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 9 Jan 2017 23:00:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-11"}
