urpose, we measure the distribution of Polyakov-loops and the Polyakov-loop\naverage, the correlation function of the Polyakov loops and the distribution of\nthe chromoelectric flux connecting a quark and antiquark in both confinement\nand deconfinement phases.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 05:52:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2017 03:59:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-16"}
