ions with\nprecisions from significantly less than 1 mas/yr to 5 mas/yr, depending on the\nobject's brightness and location on the sky.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 15:13:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 22 Feb 2017 15:51:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-29"}
